trans-unit.source: Provides programmatic access to the <see langword="urlMappings" /> configuration section.
This class cannot be inherited.
The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMappingsSection> class provides a way to programmatically access and modify the `urlMappings` section of a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMappingsSection>类使您能够以编程方式访问和修改`urlMappings`配置文件节。

trans-unit.source: The `urlMappings` section contains <xref:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMapping> objects that map URLs that are displayed to users to URLs that exist in your Web application.
trans-unit.target: `urlMappings`部分包含<xref:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMapping>映射到的 url 的 Web 应用程序中存在的用户显示的 Url 的对象。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMappingsSection> can write information into the related section of the configuration file according to the restrictions defined by the section property <xref:System.Configuration.SectionInformation.AllowDefinition%2A> whose value is <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationAllowDefinition.MachineToApplication>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMappingsSection>可以将信息写入根据定义的部分属性的限制的配置文件的相关节<xref:System.Configuration.SectionInformation.AllowDefinition%2A>其值是<xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationAllowDefinition.MachineToApplication>。

trans-unit.source: Any attempt to write in a configuration file at a level not allowed in the hierarchy will result in an error message generated by the parser.
trans-unit.target: 在层次结构不允许层次结构中的配置文件中写入任何尝试会对由分析器生成的错误消息中。

trans-unit.source: However, you can use this class to read configuration information at any level in the hierarchy.
trans-unit.target: 但是，此类可用于读取层次结构中的任何级别的配置信息。

trans-unit.source: The following code example shows how to obtain the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMappingsSection> object from the configuration file of an existing Web application.
trans-unit.target: 下面的代码示例演示如何获取<xref:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMappingsSection>从现有的 Web 应用程序的配置文件的对象。

trans-unit.source: Also shown is an excerpt of the configuration file.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMappingsSection" /> class.
The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMappingsSection.%23ctor%2A> constructor is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMappingsSection.%23ctor%2A>构造函数不应在代码中直接使用。

trans-unit.source: It is called by the ASP.NET configuration system.
trans-unit.target: 它是由 ASP.NET 配置系统调用的。

trans-unit.source: You obtain an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMappingsSection> class by using the <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.GetSection%2A> method.
Gets or sets a value indicating whether the mapping is enabled.
<see langword="true" /> if the mapping is enabled; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> 如果启用了映射;否则为<see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The default value is <see langword="true" />.
Gets a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMapping" /> objects.
A <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMappingCollection" /> that contains <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMapping" /> objects.
Each <xref:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMapping> object contains two properties identifying a URL.
trans-unit.target: 每个<xref:System.Web.Configuration.UrlMapping>对象包含两个属性标识 URL。

trans-unit.source: One property specifies the URL shown to the user; the other specifies a URL in your Web application.
trans-unit.target: 一个属性指定向用户显示的 URL其他 Web 应用程序中指定的 URL。
